    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You funnel all of your Strength into the striking section of your weapon, with all the might of the ferocious Oni. For the duration your weapon attacks with a Power weapon deal an additional 1d8 Bludgeoning damage and your Taijutsu attacks with a Power weapon have a +1 critical threat range.</p><p>At Higher Ranks: For every rank you cast this jutsu above B-Rank, increase the cost by 3, the damage die by a step and the critical threat range by +1.</p>",
